    "passives": {
      "LightningPassiveAZeusRegular": {
        "id": "LightningPassiveAZeusRegular",
        "found": true,
        "localization": {
          "name": "Godly Lightning",
          "description": "This unit's attacks ignore Guardians and heal this unit for 100% of total damage dealt.\n\nThis unit cannot be sent to the reinforcements from the battlefield.\n\nThis unit has Sleep immunity and Stun immunity. These immunity effects are removed from this unit when this unit activates Zeus's Blessing.\n\nWhen this unit takes damage from an attack, they will immediately get the next turn, this cannot trigger again until TU advances. This is a skin effect. This unit cannot become a Guardian or Stun Absorber.\n\nThis unit enters battle with 3 Charges. Certain skills are affected by and may consume charges. A unit can store a maximum of 3 charges.\n\nAt the end of this unit's turn, if this unit has exactly:\n- 3 Charges, all enemies on the battlefield that have a current TU of 50 or less are stunned for 100TU.\n- 2 Charges, all enemies on the battlefield that have a current TU of 100 or less are stunned for 200TU.\n- 1 Charge, all enemies on the battlefield that have a current TU of 200 or less are stunned for 300TU.\nThen a Charge is consumed by this unit."
        }
      },
      "ChargedUpPassiveAZeusRegular": {
        "id": "ChargedUpPassiveAZeusRegular",
        "found": true,
        "localization": {
          "name": "Omnipotence",
          "description": "If this unit would be defeated by an enemy attack or a status effect while having more than 1 HP, it instead survives with 1 HP.\n\nEach time a unit gets the turn, this unit will be healed for 30% of its max HP.\n\nAfter entering battle, this unit cannot be burned for 200TU.\n\nEach time this unit takes damage from an attack and survives until after the end of the turn, this unit will heal for 50% of its max HP and be Purified (any negative status effects like sleep, burn or poison are removed).\n\nThis unit's attack has 0.25x of their original Attack added to their Attack for each enemy on the battlefield that has a current TU of 50 or less (max of 1.0x if 4 enemies have a current TU of 50 or less). This does stack on top of Enrage effects, and other Attack increases (e.g. 1.5x + 0.25x => 1.75x total)."
        }
      },
